the pickups and the skull, so that even as

00:07:38.059 --> 00:07:42.930
they move around, it's going to be picking
up the electromagnetic activity on the surface

00:07:42.930 --> 00:07:44.439
of the brain.

00:07:44.439 --> 00:07:48.449
And that actually is remarkable that that
information is detectable, even through our

00:07:48.449 --> 00:07:49.449
