00:13:29.750 --> 00:13:33.420
And it was clear from the brain activity--I'm
sitting like, 20 feet away from them--but

00:13:33.420 --> 00:13:36.259
it's clear from the brain activity that he's
interested.

00:13:36.259 --> 00:13:38.430
He's attentive in a variety of ways.

00:13:38.430 --> 00:13:42.779
