&gt;&gt;MALE AUDIENCE MEMBER #4: Can you quantify
them into the 16 boxes of the Myers-Briggs

00:30:39.320 --> 00:30:40.320
personality?

00:30:40.320 --> 00:30:41.320
&gt;&gt;Dario Nardi: Yes.

00:30:41.320 --> 00:30:42.320
Right.

00:30:42.320 --> 00:30:43.320
Right.

00:30:43.320 --> 00:30:44.320
Right.

00:30:44.320 --> 00:30:45.320
Repeat the question.

00:30:45.320 --> 00:30:46.320
If I were to just see--.

00:30:46.320 --> 00:30:47.320
Oh, I already advanced this for a moment go
back here.

00:30:47.320 --> 00:30:48.320
If I were to just see this activity--.

00:30:48.320 --> 00:30:50.860
I would say if I'm sitting there at the computer,
I'll have some ideas.

00:30:50.860 --> 00:30:55.380
If I were to get the statistical average it
