01:08:00.780 --> 01:08:03.680
But beyond that, there might be some big differences.

01:08:03.680 --> 01:08:06.720
So, individuality still matters quite a bit.

01:08:06.720 --> 01:08:08.940
And I think that feels natural to all of us.

